=== Noun ===
'''fire''' ([[uncountable]] and [[countable]]; plural: [[fires]])

#A chemical reaction involving the bonding of [[oxygen]] with [[carbon]] and related compounds, with the production of a flame.
# Something that has or will produce this chemical reaction (like a campfire, a fireplace etc.)
#(''alchemy'') One of the four basic elements.
#The destruction of something by fire, especially when accidental.
#that in which something [[burn]]s or [[combusts]]

